# Scoped development prompt (docs mirror)

**Canonical file:** [`.cursor/rules/cursor-scoped-development-prompt.mdc`](../.cursor/rules/cursor-scoped-development-prompt.mdc)

## Two-run workflow

```txt
Run A — Phase 0 clarify (plan only, no code):
Run B — Phase 0 implement OR Phase 1 (after you approve the plan)
```

---

